M.A. Hanna Co said it has reached definitive agreement to purchase PMS Consolidated, a privatelyowned manufacturer of colorants for the plastics industry.    M.A. Hanna said the purchase, which is subject to certainconditions, is scheduled to close around the end of October.Hanna announced last August that it was in negotiaitons topurchase the company.    Headquartered in Somerset, N.J., PMS reported over 70 mlndlrs in revenues in its last fiscal year, which ended May 1987. Reuter&#3;